00:35:47.230 --> 00:35:48.170
may sariling kagustuhan.

00:35:49.190 --> 00:35:50.610
Mahilig kang gumiling ng mga damo, magluto,

00:35:50.630 --> 00:35:51.570
at maging mabuting tao.

00:35:52.150 --> 00:35:53.130
Pero ako?

00:35:53.550 --> 00:35:55.820
Gusto kong manood ng mga ibon, isda, magsaya sa musika,

00:35:55.890 --> 00:35:58.260
at mamuhay ako bilang isang walanghiyang babaero.

00:35:59.230 --> 00:36:00.130
Sa kanya-kanyang sarili.

00:36:09.460 --> 00:36:10.310
[Heyu Apothecary]

00:36:10.310 --> 00:36:10.860
